
apt-get update
apt-get upgrade

apt-get install mysql-server-5.5
	root / h#l
apt-get install tomcat7

On a Linux Debian-based (so Ubuntu included) you have also to go \
to /etc/defaults/tomcat7, uncomment the #AUTHBIND=no line and 
set its value to 'yes', in order to let the server bind on a privileged port.